        },
        {
            "title": "若合併談判成功 力拓據悉對保留嘉能可的煤炭業務持開放態度",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，力拓若與嘉能可的合併談判成功，將對保留嘉能可龐大的煤炭業務持開放態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉將標志著力拓的重大轉變，該公司曾在2018年同意出售旗下最後一批煤礦。儘管包括力拓在內的競爭對手因投資者壓力而撤出煤炭領域，嘉能可卻加倍押注這種燃料，如今已成為全球最大的煤炭生產商之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">力拓與嘉能可周四晚間宣布，正就部分或全部業務潛在合併事宜展開磋商。此次談判是礦業界併購浪潮中的最新動向，主要驅動因素是全球最大礦商紛紛尋求銅業務擴張。嘉能可擁有規模龐大且極具吸引力的銅資產，但其煤炭業務長期被視為潛在收購方的障礙。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6d42b2d7-be65-338d-b675-6caf3ea255fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：嘉能可稱與力拓就合併進行初步談判</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，交易結構與範圍仍在商討中，但考慮中的重點方案之一是收購嘉能可全部業務（含煤炭板塊）。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前尚未作出最終決定，若交易成功，力拓亦可能選擇在後期剝離煤炭業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">力拓和嘉能可的代表均拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Rio Tinto Said to Be Open to Owning Coal If It Buys Glencore</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%A5%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-%E5%8A%9B%E6%8B%93%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99%E5%98%89%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%85%A4%E7%82%AD%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E6%8C%81%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6-110739438.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-09 20:00:57",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國提供數千萬美元支持柬埔寨泰國停火協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國一位高級官員呼籲柬埔寨和泰國維護其爭議邊界沿線脆弱的停火協議，並承諾提供資金支持停火、排雷以及打擊跨國犯罪的努力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國務院負責東亞和太平洋事務的助理國務卿邁克爾·德索姆布雷周五在聲明中稱，將提供1500萬美元用於邊境穩定，1000萬美元用於排雷和清除未爆彈藥，以及2000萬美元用於幫助兩國打擊詐騙活動和毒品走私的舉措。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泰國和柬埔寨在12月27日達成停火協議。之前在7月下旬也曾達成停火協議，但後來破裂。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e8c068e8-44a0-3d06-95d0-681569f350fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Offers Millions to Support Cambodia-Thailand Ceasefire</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-082141155.html",
