        {
            "title": "法國指責美國利用貿易脅迫和制裁削弱歐洲 稱外部威脅日益嚴峻",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國指責美國利用貿易脅迫和制裁手段削弱歐洲團結與主權，該國外交部長讓-諾埃爾·巴羅警告稱，歐洲正面臨日益嚴峻的外部威脅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巴羅在巴黎向法國駐外大使發表講話時表示，敵對勢力正通過「在我們東翼的領土入侵、貿易勒索以及對格陵蘭島的主張 —— 該島不可出售」等方式考驗歐盟。他似乎將美國的行動與俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭的行為等同看待。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出，美國近期採取的經濟措施 —— 包括對歐洲企業和一位前歐盟專員實施制裁 —— 「是對我們在本土自主選擇規則能力的挑戰」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6ebbc4d7-9b48-3963-afdc-edfb7c5a78e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他警告稱：「若挑戰書已然發出，法國必將應戰。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：法國前總理稱美國對格陵蘭動武將觸及歐洲紅線 美國將因此變為敵人</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題France Warns That Europe is Under Threat From US Coercion</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%84%85%E8%BF%AB%E5%92%8C%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%89%8A%E5%BC%B1%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E5%9A%B4%E5%B3%BB-095830871.html",
